          "text": "Use a single replica of each microservice to reduce complexity",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "explanation": "Using a single replica for each microservice reduces complexity but also introduces a single point of failure. If the replica fails, the service becomes unavailable. Cloud-native architecture encourages using multiple replicas of each microservice, so traffic can be redirected if one replica fails, enhancing fault tolerance.",
