          "isCorrect": true,
          "explanation": "Taints prevent pods from being scheduled on certain nodes unless the pod has a matching toleration. The node in this scenario has a taint (high-memory:NoSchedule), which prevents pods from being scheduled unless they tolerate the taint. To resolve this issue, the pod should include a toleration in its configuration that matches the node’s taint.",
